x4freetext: NEUTRON RESONANCE PARAMETERS OF RHENIUM ISOTOPES
FAST IMPULSE REACTOR IBR-30 WITH NEUTRON
MULTIPLICATION = 100, MEAN POWER = 4 KW AND PULSE
FOUR SODIUM-IODIDE DETECTORS WERE USED FOR GAMMA
TWO LITHIUM-GLASS DETECTORS NE-908 WERE USED
FOR ENERGIES BELOW 60 EV AREA-ANALYSIS WAS USED
FOR ENERGIES ABOVE 60 EV SHAPE-ANALYSIS WAS USED
FOR BOTH AREA- AND SHAPE-ANALYSIS NEUTRON-GAMMA WIDTH
SAMPLE WEIGHT IS 59 G, RE-185 CONTENT IS 93.6 PERCENT
FLUCTUATION OF THE STRENGTH FUNCTION HAS BEEN OBSERVED
